Comment: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:03.60,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Né regole. Né comandamenti. Né ragione.
Comment: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:06.59,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}In altre parole: imprevedibile.
Comment: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:08.16,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ma succede.
Comment: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:09.39,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Cose spiacevoli succedono.
Comment: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:11.46,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}E io ne sono la causa.
Comment: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:15.04,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ancora non capisci?
Comment: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:16.30,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Niente di cui nutrirmi.
Comment: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:19.23,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mi fanno morire di fame.
Comment: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:25.50,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mi fanno morire credendo di poter prevedere.
Comment: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:34.35,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}yo wo watari yuku tsuki ni shio wa takaku michite
Comment: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:40.89,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}umineko no naku koe wa fuon no kumo wo maneku
Comment: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:47.16,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}konjiki no noroi to nokosareshi kotoba to
Comment: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:53.80,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}himeyaka na hohoemi wa kurenai ni nijimu
Comment: 0,0:00:53.80,0:01:00.54,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}tozasareta hitomi de nani wo motometeru
Comment: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:06.48,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}kowareta sono kakera wo atsumete mite mo
Comment: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:13.48,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}fureta yubi wo koboreru kimi ni todokanai
Comment: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.59,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}kazarareta kyojitsu
Comment: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:18.56,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ai ga nakereba mienai
Comment: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:26.86,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(0,2000)}Senza amore, la verità non si vede.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:03.60,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Nem as regras, nem os mandamentos, nem a razão.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:06.59,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Em outras palavras: imprevisível.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:08.16,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mas isso acontece.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:09.39,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Coisas ruins acontecem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:11.46,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}E eu sou a causa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:15.04,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ainda não entendeu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:16.30,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Nada para me alimentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:19.23,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eles me fazem morrer de fome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:25.50,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Me fazem morrer acreditando que podem prever tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:34.35,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A lua atravessa a noite e agita a maré.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:40.89,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}O choro das gaivotas atrai nuvens turbulentas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:47.16,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Uma maldição dourada, palavras deixadas para trás
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:53.80,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}e sorrisos discretos são manchados de vermelho-sangue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:01:00.54,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}O que deseja ver com esses olhos fechados?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:06.48,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mesmo que tente reunir esses fragmentos despedaçados,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:13.48,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}você nunca os alcançará enquanto escorrerem por seus dedos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.59,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sem amor não podemos ver
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:18.56,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}as verdades ornadas por falsidades.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:26.86,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(0,2000)}Sem amor, a verdade não pode ser vista.
